'''三碘化铀'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]] UI<sub>3</sub>。 它是一种黑色固体，可溶于水。

==制备==
三碘化铀可以由碘和铀直接化合而成:<ref name="brauer">Georg Brauer (ed.): ''Handbuch der Präparativen Anorganischen Chemie''. 3rd edition. Vol. 2, Enke, Stuttgart 1978, {{ISBN|3-432-87813-3}}, p. 1218.</ref>

:2 U + 3 I<sub>2</sub> → 2 UI<sub>3</sub>

如果在反应时接触到[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]] (thf)，产物会是蓝色的加合物 UI<sub>3</sub>(thf)<sub>4</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Lewis Base Adducts of Uranium Triiodide and Tris[Bis(Trimethylsilyl)Amido]Uranium|journal=Inorg. Synth.|volume=31|authors=
David L. Clark, Alfred P. Sattelberger|pages=307–315|year=1997|doi=10.1002/9780470132623.ch55}}</ref>

==性质==
它的[[空间群|空间群]]是 ''C''cm''m'' ，[[晶格参数|晶格参数]]为 ''a'' = 432.8 pm, ''b'' = 1401.1 pm, 和 ''c'' = 1000.5 pm <ref name="Structure">J. H. Levy, J. C. Taylor, P. W. Wilson: "The Structure of Uranium(III) Triiodide by Neutron Diffraction", in: ''[[Acta_Crystallogr._B|Acta Crystallogr. B]]'', '''1975''', ''31'', S. 880–882 ({{DOI|10.1107/S0567740875003986}}).</ref>。

三碘化铀是[[路易斯酸|路易斯酸]]。<ref>Jacqueline Collin, Leonor Maria, Isabel Santos: "Uranium Iodides as Catalysts for Diels–Alder Reactions", in: ''[[Journal_of_Molecular_Catalysis_A:_Chemical|Journal of Molecular Catalysis A: Chemical]]'', '''2000''', ''160'' (2), pp. 263–267 ({{DOI|10.1016/S1381-1169(00)00257-0}}).</ref>

